                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Crisis is a Hair</l>
                    <l>Toward which forces<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 creep </l>
                    <l>Past which - forces<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 retrogade </l>
                    <l>If it come in sleep </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To suspend the Breath</l>
                    <l>Is the most we can </l>
                    <l>Ignorant is it Life or Death </l>
                    <l>Nicely balancing - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Let an instant push </l>
                    <l>Or an Atom press</l>
                    <l>Or a Circle hesitate </l>
                    <l>In Circumference </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It may jolt the Hand </l>
                    <l>That adjusts the Hair </l>
                    <l>That secures Eternity</l>
                    <l>From presenting - Here - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
